					<description><![CDATA[Nice metaphor ,

I reminds me of the effects of alcohol. 

If you have a hangover you need time to recuperate, lots of water and rest.  A hangover once a year is not problem.  You  will loose some time, productivity but you have  enjoyed had a nice evening.  

If you have a drinking problem water and rest will not solve it. You need something else.  The cumulative effect is devastating. 

The cumulative effect is also an excellent force.

JOhan DHAeseleer - Jodha the todo master]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Nice metaphor ,</p>
<p>I reminds me of the effects of alcohol. </p>
<p>If you have a hangover you need time to recuperate, lots of water and rest.  A hangover once a year is not problem.  You  will loose some time, productivity but you have  enjoyed had a nice evening.  </p>
<p>If you have a drinking problem water and rest will not solve it. You need something else.  The cumulative effect is devastating. </p>
<p>The cumulative effect is also an excellent force.</p>
<p>JOhan DHAeseleer &#8211; Jodha the todo master</p>
